data.name: RestoreButton.ToolTipText
data.value:
Restore Savegame from Backup
Restore the savegame loded on the left, with a backup, selected on the right. (Warning it's recommended to do a backup, before restoring anything, if the latest backup isn't matching your savegame version)

data.name: $this.ToolTip
data.value: Restores the selected Backup by replacing the existing savegame files with the files you made a backup of earlier. Your current savegame state will be deleted, so if you haven't, got yet, hit the backup button once more beforehand!
